mig.description:
In December 2015, the Municipality of Hissarya signed a contract for the provision of grants № RD 50-211 / 07.12.2015 under sub-measure 19.1 "Assistance for preparatory activities" of measure 19 "Community-led local development" of the Development Program of Rural Areas 2014-2020 (RDP). Partners of the Municipality of Hissarya in the implementation of the project are the Community Center "Ivan Vazov - 1904", Cooperative "Agrocommerce - 98". The project has a total value of BGN 58,674.90, and its implementation period is from December 7, 2015 to September 7, 2016. Within the project, studies and analyzes of the territory will be carried out, necessary for the preparation of a Strategy for local development, organization and conduct of information campaigns, trainings of the LAG team, incl. representatives of the partners and local leaders from the municipalities of Hissarya. The main results that will be achieved in the implementation of project activities are: 
• Registered non-profit association "Local Initiative Group - Hissarya", which will include members of the business, non-profit and public sector of the municipality of Hissarya; 
• Prepared Strategy for community-led local development (CLLD) with a territorial scope, including the municipality of Hissarya.
